						<div class="postbody">I think the 1-line 8-pixel-off artifacts are because the coarse scroll (X bits 8-3) needs to go in earlier than the fine scroll (X bits 2-0). So you're seeing one scanline's coarse scroll with another line's fine scroll.</div>

